{"tid":1344182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(前線感受)「光復香港！時代革命！」以武制暴！","createTime":"2019-07-21T20:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:36:51.000Z","uid":2719,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3705ff6a924c4f27799ed2d8f146fd7eaf93696d","tid":1344182,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KfUiL4p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKfUiL4p.png&h=5cfe1798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好再嗌乜香港人加油<br />\n五大訴求 係乞求<br />\n時代革命 係主動<br />\n我地無得再退 要勇武抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n以前大家俾黑警打 擋 依家識還手<br />\n今晚大家俾黑社會打 擋 下次就識團結還手<br />\n黑警都敢打 唔洗怕黑社會！<br />\n<br />\n唔可以成日靠最前嘅勇者<br />\n大佬你地走緊嗰時 勇者仲係上環<br />\n你地真係要學識保護自己 保護身邊嘅人<br />\n<br />\n始終有一日要打大佬 要全城勇武<br />\n依家係時候壯下膽 時日無多<br />\n俾你地玩盡都係去到2022 就全面監控<br />\n所以大家係時後醒覺<br />\n<br />\n成立臨時立法會/政府 唔好再講乜春無可能<br />\n要諗下點樣變成有可能 <br />\n只要大家團結 就會有奇蹟岀現 加油！"},{"pid":"d96a2626795a661ecc5a5b7351397f1c740e667b","tid":1344182,"uid":151583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:56:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db11e283b3ab141a6c24ad966d65b7fdc2b59dcc","tid":1344182,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:59:38.000Z","msg":"一定要贏"},{"pid":"23f0e3770efd534d2e7bc8627205bb9c1606ac7e","tid":1344182,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmo